  457|       |        //     in the same units (items from the *start* of the sequence,
  458|       |        //     not from the clone's view), so the definite-length
  459|       |        //     termination check `self.parsed >= count` in `at_end` keeps
  460|       |        //     working as the clone advances `parsed`. Carrying `count`
